            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1462,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01GcEnXLyWtCv2SFV2JzaLeo\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Great question! After you launch your Google Ads campaign, here's what happens next:\\n\\n**1. Traffic Flows In** — Your ads start showing to people searching for scheduling solutions, and clicks drive visitors to your landing page.\\n\\n**2. You Measure Results** — Google Ads tracks conversions (sign-ups, demo requests, etc.) so you can see if people are actually excited about your product.\\n\\n**3. You Iterate** — Based on what's working, you can:\\n   - Pause underperforming ads\\n   - Double down on high-converting headlines/descriptions\\n   - Adjust your budget to focus on winning keywords\\n   - Test new messaging to improve your conversion rate\\n\\n**The Goal**: Validate whether your scheduling tool solves a real problem people will pay for. If your ads get clicks and conversions, you've got product-market fit. If not, you learn what messaging resonates and try again.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Ready to build your first ad campaign?** I can help you create compelling headlines, descriptions, and other ad assets to get started. Just let me know! 🚀\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1649,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":244,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
